snippet.title: WARSAW Reveal Trailer | WWII rpg strategy game announcement
snippet.description:
WARSAW is a brand new tactical rpg set in a war-torn European capital during WWII.
Wishlist it on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1026420/WARSAW/

Coming in Q3'2019 to PC, PS4, Switch.

Homepage: http://warsawthegame.com/
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/Warsawthegame-398918990923030/
Twitter: https://twitter.com/warsawthegame

© 2018, 2019 Pixelated Milk / gaming company

Cinematic produced by Human Ark
Music editing: Mariusz Szypura
Sound engineering: Studio Soundmaking

Music: Varsovie by Brodka © Kayax Production and Publishing
Composed by: Bartosz Dziedzic, Monika Brodka
Lyrics by: Monika Brodka, Quentin Carenzo
